Tests for brp-mangle-shebangs

Usage:

    $ python3.7 -m venv __venv__
    $ . __venv__/bin/activate
    (__venv__) $ python -m pip install pytest
    (__venv__) $ python -m pytest -v test_brp_mangle_shebangs.py

